oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (red, black and green on white) announcing All for the Hall with Keith Urban, Vince Gill, Rascal Flatts, Lady Antebellum, Alabama, Alison Krauss and the Union Station, Pistol Annies, the Band Perry, the Oak Ridge Boys, Little Big Town, Thompson Square, Diamond Rio, Exile, and the Blue Sky Riders at the Bridgestone Arena on April 10.
